---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Micromega - Tavola rotonda | Guido Chiesa" description="2002 — articolo">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-zinc-400">2002 — articolo</div>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.06em] text-zinc-900 sm:text-5xl">Micromega - Tavola rotonda</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="prose-guido space-y-5 text-base leading-8 text-zinc-700">
      <p>Dibattito organizzato dalla rivista Micromega con Mimmo Calopresti e Gabriele Muccino, coordinato da Oscar Iarussi</p>
        
<h2>Download</h2>
<ul class="downloads">
     
        <li><a href="http://guidochiesa.net/media/opera/guido-chiesa/tavola-rotonda/Tavola rotonda.pdf">Tavola rotonda.pdf</a></li>
    
</ul>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 border-t border-zinc-100 pt-8">
      <a href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "testi/"} class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 transition hover:text-emerald-800">&larr; Torna ai testi</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
